 />\nMade in 🇧🇪</blockquote><br />\noralb pro600 德國版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3138a3b4a3bff427e18d209679b0ab7fd5ea6d6b","tid":360772,"uid":126293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Philips soniccare 好耐用的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 已用左三十幾年,刷頭都冇換過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩屌，三十幾年？邊隻MODEL咁好？<br />\n我上台灣網班人成日話過左保養，2-3年D電就唔太掂了...</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://photos1.blogger.com/blogger/7057/1208/1600/967.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotos1.blogger.com%2Fblogger%2F7057%2F1208%2F1600%2F967.jpeg&h=df14dff7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9874488ed76ffa6b580b0dcb86525774bb8489ed","tid":360772,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Philips soniccare 好耐用的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 已用左三十幾年,刷頭都冇換過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩屌，三十幾年？邊隻MODEL咁好？<br />\n我上台灣網班人成日話過左保養，2-3年D電就唔太掂了...</blockquote><br />\n三十幾年既電動牙刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  影黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9141d1204dc447a2f80223aebfe15ea78fc28edc","tid":360772,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:03:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Philips soniccare 好耐用的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 已用左三十幾年,刷頭都冇換過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩屌，三十幾年？邊隻MODEL咁好？<br />\n我上台灣網班人成日話過左保養，2-3年D電就唔太掂了...</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://photos1.blogger.com/blogger/7057/1208/1600/967.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotos1.blogger.com%2