uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己做緊ORAL CARE呢個film<br />\n<br />\n每年都要睇美國牙醫報告<br />\n轉動牙刷轉力太大會做成琺瑯質磨損<br />\n報告都係建議用番手動/ 聲波<br />\n<br />\n你自己去retail store玩下聲波/轉動牙刷<br />\n轉動牙刷好大力好傷琺瑯質同牙肉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉動刷頭輕輕貼住隻牙就得，要控制力度，有d model有壓力提示，同埋唔好刷咁耐，會刷蝕棚牙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n轉動牙刷龍頭oralB 親身回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對唔住大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa909571816aae5f30f3cbb1923802ce5baafef","tid":360772,"uid":73748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:35:07.000Z","msg":"用緊Philips Sonicare Healthy White<br />\n<br />\n牙科護士話呢枝加埋牙線已經足夠"},{"pid":"9ef0b3a3be25288ddad25d5fdeccb971419154c6","tid":360772,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己做緊ORAL CARE呢個film<br />\n<br />\n每年都要睇美國牙醫報告<br />\n轉動牙刷轉力太大會做成琺瑯質磨損<br />\n報告都係建議用番手動/ 聲波<br />\n<br />\n你自己去retail store玩下聲波/轉動牙刷<br />\n轉動牙刷好大力好傷琺瑯質同牙肉</blockquote><br />\n咁補過牙果啲位，係咪唔啱用電動牙刷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事關我補左好多隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人建議你自己落街拎2支野玩下<br />\n要刷乾淨排牙雖然好重要, 但重點係唔好刷傷排牙<br />\n<br />\n我自己都有個位補牙, 補牙都好硬淨, 呢個位我又唔擔心<br />\n<br />\n重有, 牙膏唔好揀美白<br />\n你用完美白牙膏刷牙, 會feel到有啲粒子係口腔度, (好似啲好幼好幼好幼既沙咁)<br />\n其實係啲粒子打磨你既牙<br />\n好傷琺瑯質<br />\n<br />\n個人推薦用番oral B最普遍個隻牙膏, 十幾蚊, 唔好搞咁多野<br />\n個人推薦唔好用力加牙膏"},{"pid":"5f2158df9d5a33dae62621984fa88c9e1cdc2cad","tid":360772,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇中Philips soniccare，不過唔知邊隻好...<br />\n仲有佢果隻水牙線...<br />\n<br />\n不過聽聞呢d電動牙刷換唔到電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n粒電兩年幾三年好快打柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換電果d又唔多夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無邊款耐用推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n價錢唔係最大問題，唔想隔幾年換一支新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我兩年前買過panasonic 水牙線，我覺得冇用。有時唔小心射到喉嚨好痛，用左兩個星期冇用，都係用番普通牙線。"},{"pid":"ce22f58f46ab3f6dc0757d8c9f8c170678d28df3","tid":360772,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Philips soniccare 好耐用的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 已用左三十幾年,刷頭都冇換過</blockquote><br />\n三十幾年唔換頭？"},{"pid":"b27b772057a8af0abe3a6476cb6fc796f9f87b73","tid":360772,"uid":19538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T08:35:09.000Z","msg":"你地覺得壓力感應重唔重要？<br />\n聽人講電動牙刷唔可以太大力放落牙到，唔係架話好易傷到牙<br />\n<br />\n驚眼訓得滯大力左都唔知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31aa7d5ffa4bdf8cfbf0aae7ea3ec5744bd2b22","tid":360772,"uid":19538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T08:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇中Philips soniccare，不過唔知邊隻好...<br />\n仲有佢果隻水牙線...<br />\n<br />\n不過聽聞呢d電動牙刷換唔到電<img src=\"/ass